Description: X.Org X server -- WonderMedia WM8505 (GE 2D) display driver
 This package provides the "wmt" DDX driver for WMT OS.  It drives the
 WonderMedia WM8505 display controller through the in-kernel wmt-drm
 KMS device and accelerates 2D solid fills and copies on the WM8505
 Graphics Engine (GE) via the EXA acceleration architecture.
